pma:database.name: investiclub
pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `brokers` ( `broker_id` smallint(5) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `url` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `image` blob, `autocomplete` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0', `last_update` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, PRIMARY KEY (`broker_id`), UNIQUE KEY `name_UNIQUE` (`name`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `clubs` ( `club_id` mediumint(8) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `club_name` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `broker_id` smallint(5) unsigned NOT NULL, `currency` char(3) NOT NULL, `club_registration_date` date NOT NULL, `club_dissolution_date` date DEFAULT NULL, `payment_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL, `payment_type` varchar(25) DEFAULT NULL, `payment_months` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL, `active` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1', `created_on` datetime NOT NULL, `last_update` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, PRIMARY KEY (`club_id`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=12 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `club_settings` ( `club_id` mediumint(8) unsigned NOT NULL, `min_members` smallint(6) DEFAULT '0', `max_members` smallint(6) DEFAULT '0', `transaction_fee_flat` float DEFAULT '0', `transaction_fee_percent` float DEFAULT '0', `min_contribution` float DEFAULT '0', `max_contribution` float DEFAULT '0', PRIMARY KEY (`club_id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `club_users` ( `club_id` mediumint(8) unsigned NOT NULL, `user_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL, `role` varchar(65) NOT NULL, `enrollement_date` date NOT NULL, `departure_date` date DEFAULT NULL, `active` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `created_on` datetime NOT NULL, `last_update` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, PRIMARY KEY (`club_id`,`user_id`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `logs` ( `log_id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `user_id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL, `time` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, `type` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `description` varchar(255) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`log_id`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `permissions` ( `permission_id` smallint(5) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `resource` varchar(65) NOT NULL, `privilege` varchar(65) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`permission_id`), UNIQUE KEY `member_id` (`resource`,`privilege`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `stats_cache` ( `stat_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `session_id` int(11) NOT NULL, `validity` int(11) NOT NULL, `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, `scope` varchar(8) NOT NULL, `key` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `full_key` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `size` mediumint(9) NOT NULL, `action` varchar(45) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`stat_id`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=565 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `treasury_balance_sheet` ( `balancesheet_id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `club_id` mediumint(8) unsigned NOT NULL, `balance` float NOT NULL, `portfolio` float NOT NULL, `profit` float NOT NULL, `date` date NOT NULL, `last_update` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, PRIMARY KEY (`balancesheet_id`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=14 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `treasury_capital_users` ( `capital_id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `user_id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL, `balance_sheet_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL, `capital` float NOT NULL, `profit` float NOT NULL, `last_update` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, PRIMARY KEY (`capital_id`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=72 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `treasury_cashflow` ( `cashflow_id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `club_id` mediumint(8) unsigned NOT NULL, `user_id` int(10) unsigned DEFAULT NULL, `type` enum('debit','credit') NOT NULL, `value` float DEFAULT NULL, `comment` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `date` date NOT NULL, `last_update` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, PRIMARY KEY (`cashflow_id`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=84 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `treasury_departure` ( `departure_id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `user_id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL, `club_id` mediumint(8) unsigned NOT NULL, `date` date NOT NULL, `last_update` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, PRIMARY KEY (`departure_id`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `treasury_revaluation` ( `revaluation_id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `club_id` mediumint(8) unsigned NOT NULL, `value` float NOT NULL, `comment` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `date` date NOT NULL, `last_update` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, PRIMARY KEY (`revaluation_id`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `treasury_transactions` ( `transaction_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `club_id` mediumint(8) unsigned NOT NULL, `type` enum('buy','sell','dividend') NOT NULL, `share` varchar(65) DEFAULT NULL, `quantity` mediumint(8) unsigned NOT NULL, `value` float NOT NULL, `gain` float NOT NULL, `currency` char(3) NOT NULL, `date` date NOT NULL, `last_update` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, PRIMARY KEY (`transaction_id`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=44 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `users` ( `user_id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `email` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `password` char(128) NOT NULL, `last_name` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `first_name` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `gender` enum('M','F') DEFAULT NULL, `address` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL, `city` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL, `postal_code` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL, `country` char(2) NOT NULL, `phone_mobile` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `phone_home` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `date_of_birth` date DEFAULT NULL, `occupation` varchar(45) DEFAULT NULL, `active` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `created_on` datetime NOT NULL, `last_login` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, PRIMARY KEY (`user_id`), UNIQUE KEY `email_UNIQUE` (`email`), KEY `idx_fk_email` (`email`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=120 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `user_settings` ( `user_id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL, `locale` varchar(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'en_US', `currency` char(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'EUR' COMMENT 'Currency code that follows ISO 4217 standard.', `timezone` varchar(45) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'UTC', `last_update` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, PRIMARY KEY (`user_id`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
